@startuml PTaaS_Engagement_States

' ============================================
' STATE DIAGRAM: PTaaS Engagement Lifecycle
' Bug Bounty and Its Simulation Platform
' ============================================

title PTaaS Engagement State Transitions

[*] --> Draft : Organization creates engagement

Draft --> Published : Publish engagement
Draft --> [*] : Cancel draft

Published --> Inviting : Send researcher invitations
Inviting --> Assigned : Researcher(s) accepted
Inviting --> Cancelled : No responses (timeout)

Assigned --> In_Progress : Engagement started
In_Progress --> Testing : Active testing phase
Testing --> Reporting : Testing complete
Reporting --> Review : Report submitted

Review --> Retest_Required : Fixes needed
Review --> Completed : Report approved

Retest_Required --> Testing : Retest scheduled
Completed --> Payment_Pending : Approve payment
Payment_Pending --> Paid : Payment processed
Paid --> Closed : Engagement archived

Cancelled --> [*]
Closed --> [*]

note right of Published
  Engagement details:
  - Scope & timeline
  - Budget
  - Required skills
end note

note right of Testing
  Active phase:
  - Researcher testing
  - Finding submission
  - Real-time updates
end note

note right of Retest_Required
  Verification needed:
  - Fixes implemented
  - Retest scheduled
  - Same researcher
end note

note right of Completed
  Deliverables:
  - Final report
  - Executive summary
  - Recommendations
end note

@enduml